These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: mirinda, almond-milk
Movie-Genre: time-travel, romance
Sport: cricket, climbing
Transport: helicopter, roller
1. Transport:roller is on the left or right of Sport:climbing##3
2. Beverage:almond-milk is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:romance == Beverage:mirinda##1
4. Transport:roller is on the right of Transport:helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | mirinda  | almond-milk   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance     | time-travel   |
| Sport         | climbing | cricket |
| Transport     | helicopter | roller    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
Food: banana, mango
Movie-Genre: sports, spy
Pet: chinchilla, horse
Transport: van, ship
1. Pet:horse is in an odd position##4
2. Movie-Genre:sports == Transport:ship##1
3. Food:mango is on the right of Movie-Genre:spy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | banana     | mango |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | sports  |
| Pet           | horse         | chinchilla     |
| Transport     | van   | ship    |

 #################################
 
